window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Adam Diehl is an 11-year-old in crisis. He knows his parents are going to split up - today - and he'd do anything in his power to stop them. If only he could turn back time....</p> <p>As it turns out, he can.</p> <p>What his parents don't know - what his sister and brother would never suspect - is that Adam is a genius, and the computer he stares at all day has opened a gateway to knowledge beyond our comprehension.</p> <p>But not Adam's.</p> <p>Now, he has a plan. He's going to repeat this day over and over until he finds the version of it that ends with his parents staying together. But he can't keep resetting the day forever.</p> <p>Because the laws of time are strict, and they're starting to push back.</p>"; 
